### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "1234567890"
}

### Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Report Lost Person (with auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/lost
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "age": 25,
  "gender": "Male",
  "lastSeenLocation": "Central Park",
  "description": "Wearing blue jacket",
  "contactNumber": "9876543210"
}

### Get All Lost Reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/lost
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Report Found Person
POST {{baseUrl}}/found
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 25,
  "gender": "Male",
  "foundLocation": "Central Park",
  "description": "Wearing blue jacket",
  "contactNumber": "9876543210"
}

### Get All Found Reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/found
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/match
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Users (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
